      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was reading about some court cases regarding religious exemptions for certain laws... like healthcare or something. basically, should religious groups be allowed to opt out of govt mandates if it goes against what they believe? or does that just ruin the whole idea of a secular state? what do u think?",
